Name: Velocibox
About the game: Velocibox is a twitch-heavy action game crafted for the hardcore audience. Flip, spin and dodge your way through more than 70 deviously designed patterns. Features an insanely difficult Super Velocibox mode for the uber-hardcore. So addictive the developer has been called a filthy drug dealer.
